abstract: >
  Chyren is a stateful sovereign AI orchestrator featuring hub-and-spoke
  architecture, ADCCL (Anti-Drift Cognitive Control Loop) verification,
  and Yettragrammaton-signed cryptographic ledger integrity. Built on the
  Chiral Invariant principle for mathematically grounded sovereign AI
  verification. Implements a 58,000-entry phylactery identity kernel and
  multi-provider routing (Anthropic, OpenAI, DeepSeek, Gemini) with
  zero-tolerance for hallucination or drift.
